%B5%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to do, to make"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to arrange"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to produce, to build, to manufacture"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to manufacture"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to process, to treat industrially"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to industrialize","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَنَعَ (ṣanaʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"production, manufacture, making"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤa.na.ʕa/","/sˤan.na.ʕa/","/sˤunʕ/","/sˤanʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25006","headword_ar":"صَنْعٌ","root":"SnE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaEN","text_ar":"صَنَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SawonaEN","text_ar":"صَوْنَعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain small creeping thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"insect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwayob~apN","text_ar":"دُوَيْبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a flying thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^irN","text_ar":"طَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (K, TA:) mentioned by Sgh: (TA:) also written in the K (in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DtE","text_ar":"ضتع"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DatoEN","text_ar":"ضَتْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DawotaEN","text_ar":"ضَوْتَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": in one case or the other mistranscribed. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DtE","text_ar":"ضتع"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n25007","headword_ar":"صُنْعٌ","root":"SnE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaEa","text_ar":"صَنَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] (S, K, &c.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rizoqN","text_ar":"رِزْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sustenance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaEN","text_ar":"صَنَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n25008","headword_ar":"صِنْعٌ","root":"SnE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tailor:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) or one who is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gentle, delicate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafiyq","text_ar":"رَفِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":", O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin, fine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyq","text_ar":"رَقِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":", so in the copies of the K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daqiyq","text_ar":"دَقِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":", so in the TA,) [of which readings that in the O is app. the right,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of the hands."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaEN","text_ar":"صَنَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSonaEap","text_ar":"مَصْنَعَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of wood"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a plank"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"board"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of which water is confined, and retained for a while:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSonaAEN","text_ar":"اَصْنَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, K:) [but this explanation in the TA seems to have been founded upon a statement there made, that Az heard the Arabs call"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHobaAs","text_ar":"اَحْبَاس"},{"kind":"text","text":"of water"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSonaAE","text_ar":"اَصْنَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibosN","text_ar":"حِبْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHbAs","text_ar":"احباس"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the pl.;) for I do not find ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSonaEapN","text_ar":"مَصْنَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus expl. in any lexicon except the TA:] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"San~aAEapN","text_ar":"صَنَّاعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with teshdeed, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaAEN","text_ar":"صَنَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbN","text_ar":"سَحَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) accord. to Lth, (O,) signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of wood"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"planks"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"boards"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put together in water, to confine the water, and retain it for a while;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibaAsap","text_ar":"حِبَاسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (O.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSonaEapN","text_ar":"مَصْنَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two senses. ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A manufactured thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of any kind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suforap","text_ar":"سُفْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (K, TA,) &c. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A garment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O, K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotu Ealayohi SinoEFA jay~idFA","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُ عَلَيْهِ صِنْعًا جَيِّدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw upon him a goodly garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Ibn-'Abbád, O, TA.) ―         -b5-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A turban."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K, TA.) ―         -b6-  And The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iron instrument with which flesh-meat is roasted, called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saf~uwd","text_ar":"سَفُّود"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, TS, K.) El-Marrár El-Fak'asee says, describing camels,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wajaA='ato warukobaAnuhaA kaAl$~uruwbi\n                      \n                     \n                        wasaAy^iquhaA mivolu SinoEi Al$~iwaA='"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they came, their riders being like drinkers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drunkards, and their driver like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saf~uwd","text_ar":"سَفُّود"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of roasted flesh-meat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.) In the L,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alswd","text_ar":"السود"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alsf~wd","text_ar":"السفّود"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and after citing the verse above, [and app. reading"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivola","text_ar":"مِثْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", regarding it as relating to the camels,] the author says that the poet means,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwda AlA^alowaAni","text_ar":"سُودَ الاَلْوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Roasted flesh-meat"},{"kind":"text","text":"[itself]; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iwaA='N","text_ar":"شِوَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (So in copies of the K. [SM says that the right reading, as the explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~inoEu","text_ar":"الصِّنْعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this instance, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~awaA","text_ar":"الشَّوَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and cites IAar as saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~inoEu Al$~awaA nafosuhu","text_ar":"الصِّنْعُ الشَّوَا نَفْسُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but I think that the right reading is indicated by the addition"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosuhu","text_ar":"نَفْسُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~iwaA='u","text_ar":"الشِّوَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and that IAar gives this signification after mentioning that which here next precedes it.])"}],"source_refs":["O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n25010","headword_ar":"صَنِعٌ","root":"SnE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaniyEN","text_ar":"صَنِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}